teamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004610/extras/984af4dc2ee45e876940a854772102f1.webp?t=1747869943\" width=424 height=58 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004610/extras/7fdb6891ecb1492eea20a70695c4f307.poster.avif?t=1747869943\" width=374 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004610/extras/7fdb6891ecb1492eea20a70695c4f307.webm?t=1747869943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004610/extras/7fdb6891ecb1492eea20a70695c4f307.mp4?t=1747869943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Hack smart-home gadgets like lights, doors and various appliances to set up traps, or improvise weapons from objects around the house. Hide under furniture, set your trajectory and plow into your enemies, munching them up once they’re knocked down.<br><br>Make sure you don’t leave too much blood on the carpet; you’ll need to make sure the house is clean before the family gets home. Only you can save Christmas and show these burglars that justice sucks!<br><br>This is a short experimental game featuring 6 difficulty scenarios set in one stage and an unlockable gallery of concept art.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NEW IN STEAM RELEASE</h2>Steam release adds achievements, controller support and 3 additional silly bonus scenarios.",
